metadata.name: YOUNG ROMANS - men portrait 01: Annibale
metadata.description:
YOUNG ROMANS - men portrait 01: Annibale

unique AI Art by Lassinger
5000 x 5000 pixel jpeg

- - -

as a great friend of italian neorealism in film and in art in general, i had been thinking about a portrait series in this direction for a long time. the older i got, the more themes like home, roots, realistic life and authenticity became the focus of my interest. respect for the lives of simple people.

these portraits were created with the help of AI in the first step and then elaborately processed and represent a unique and outstanding AI art. Collectors should make an effort to find them.
